SIMPLE: lumpectomy
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lumpectomy
<hw>Lump*ec"to*my</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>the removal
of a cyst or tumor from the breast by surgery. This is one method of
treating breast tumors when in an early stage, and is preferred for
cosmetic reasons, when medically feasible, to <contr>radical
mastectomy</contr>, the removal of the entire breast along with nearby
muscles.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>lumpen</ent>⟦br⟧
